trans-unit.source: Health model
trans-unit.target: Health model

trans-unit.source: Service Fabric introduces a health model that provides a rich, flexible and extensible reporting and evaluation functionality for Service Fabric entities.
trans-unit.target: Service Fabric introduces a health model that provides a rich, flexible and extensible reporting and evaluation functionality for Service Fabric entities.

trans-unit.source: Service Fabric components report health out of the box on all entities.
trans-unit.target: Service Fabric components report health out of the box on all entities.

trans-unit.source: User services can enrich the health data with information specific to their logic, reported on themselves or other entities in the cluster.
trans-unit.target: User services can enrich the health data with information specific to their logic, reported on themselves or other entities in the cluster.
